snippet.title: Arcade Game: Moon Cresta (1980 Nichibutsu)
snippet.description: A unique shooting game where a space is split into 3 and only one can shoot at a time. After completing, you connect your other spaceship and after shooting all aliens, you connect the thrid one and all 3 are connected. All 3 ships teamed up to fight the aliens.
